<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="therefore-adv">therefore <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ðeəfɔː(r)/    美 /'ðerfɔːr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-thus">1.★ <strong>因此；所以(thus)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think, therefore I am.
我思故我在。</p><footer>—— 笛卡尔</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We don’t need to do so much homework. Therefore, we have more time for after-school activities.
我们不需要做太多作业，因此，有更多的时间参加课外活动。</p><footer>2014全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It’s our hope that we will play a greater role in the market place and, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (因此), supply more jobs.  （2014 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. therefore  </p></div>